1.  Compile the module in a terminal

  $ make

2.  Install the module

  $ sudo insmod klogger.ko

3.  List installed modules to verify it loaded correctly

  $ lsmod

4.  Type something on the keyboard

5.  To view the keylogger file type:

  $ cat /proc/cpuinfo

6.  Remove the module

  $ sudo rmmod klogger

